
0.5.4
---
Feature
- Support remove action for RibbonQuickAccessBar/RibbonButtonGroup

Interface
- Change isHaveOptionAction to hasOptionAction for RibbonGroup
- Change RibbonSubElement.. to RibbonElement.. for RibbonManager
- Add resizeRibbon for RibbonBar
- Add setIconSize/iconSize, rename getter, remove hasWidget for RibbonCtlContainer

Bugfix
- Fix the text rect of arrow button
- Fix customize controls were executed every time

Other
- Optimize controls
- Redefine version variable


0.5.3
---
Feature
- Support user customize theme
- Optimize dark theme to cover more widgets


0.5.2
---
Feature
- Support dark theme
- Only customize widgets with title

Interface
- Add isPageContextCoverTab, setPageContextCoverTab for RibbonBar
- Remove windowTitleTextColor, setWindowTitleTextColor for RibbonBar

Bugfix
- Fix abnormal show of app button after RibbonWindow init (#I7C31M)
- Fix frameless show after setting standard QMenuBar (#I7CDUT)


0.5.1
---
Feature
- Support Application Widget
- Support FrameWindow (native Mainwindow)
- Support Qt 6.5.1
- Support PyQt5 (PyRibbon 0.1.0)
- support linux (openEuler/Ubuntu)
- Support cmake builder

Bugfix
- Fix tab text is not centered (#I7AJ9E)
- Fix RibbonGalleryGroup item border size is too large
- Fix attribute Qt::AA_EnableHighDpiScaling position error
- Fix RibbonButton not refreshing in 2row mode (#I79XLL)
- Fix taskbar is covered when maximized (win10, #I771WR)

Note
- Don't support Qt 4


